    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for someone looking for a reliable project or a budget-friendly daily driver. The engine and transmission are functional, though you may notice some minor leaks and typical wear expected for its age. The exterior shows its history with some noticeable scratches, small dings, and fading paint in certain areas, while the interior has some staining and wear on the upholstery. It has been a dependable car for us, but it will likely require some maintenance and cosmetic care in the near future to bring it back to its best.",
      "price": 19500.0,
